{"tid":2463836,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉：禁止以BNO申請工作假期市民登機返港","createTime":"2021-03-27T04:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T04:58:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"217c3fdd59cc76ddf67dce65ee594b8ebff68fa7","tid":2463836,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:15:54.000Z","msg":"港府近日透過駐港總領事館，致函14個與香港簽訂工作假期計劃協議的國家，要求不再承認BN(O)為申請簽證文件。保安局前局長、行政會議成員葉劉淑儀今早在商台節目，建議港府要求航空公司拒絕以BN(O)申請工作假期簽證的香港永久居民登機返港，必須他們出示身份證或特區護照才放行，反問這樣做「有咩問題」。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉稱，相信港府與那些國家簽訂協議時，沒有列明認可甚麼證明文件。如果港府表明不承認BN(O)，而申請者是香港永久居民，他們仍有方法回港，影響不大，「但表態係必須」。她又指，在英國推出BN(O)簽證前，BN(O)不太受歡迎，簽發量比特區護照低，公務員亦「唔睺」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社前日率先引述港府去信駐港總領事館的消息，並引述一名西方國家的高級外交官表示，香港無權要求外國政府認可哪些證件，相信大多數國家會無視信件。英國外交部其後亦回應指，港府無權要求其他國家承認指定護照，英國會繼續簽發BN(O)，並承認為有效旅遊證件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/27115741/image1616817449340.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F27115741%2Fimage1616817449340.png&h=a33db011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/325488/葉劉倡禁bno申工作假期市民登機返港%E3%80%80出示身份證/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F325488%2F%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%E5%80%A1%E7%A6%81bno%E7%94%B3%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%81%87%E6%9C%9F%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E7%99%BB%E6%A9%9F%E8%BF%94%E6%B8%AF%25E3%2580%2580%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BA%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AD%89%2F&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWooP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=d5255f17\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/325488/葉劉倡禁bno申工作假期市民登機返港%E3%80%80出示身份證/</a>"},{"pid":"5ad86e2642222b0b7b3a43add15af5bf3c6d7d74","tid":2463836,"uid":33028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:16:49.000Z","msg":"唔係1月31日開始已經話唔可以用BNO登機?"},{"pid":"03351ca21b3aa7c18746b789d7ad129d78285216","tid":2463836,"uid":188482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ad86e2642222b0b7b3a43add15af5bf3c6d7d74","tid":2463836,"uid":33028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:16:49.000Z","msg":"唔係1月31日開始已經話唔可以用BNO登機?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:18:18.000Z","msg":"個陣應該講緊出境？而家講緊係外國上機？？"},{"pid":"5914d9a279bb74158d949ba9512b84fcca3f501d","tid":2463836,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ad86e2642222b0b7b3a43add15af5bf3c6d7d74","tid":2463836,"uid":33028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:16:49.000Z","msg":"唔係1月31日開始已經話唔可以用BNO登機?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:19:19.000Z","msg":"外國機場登機"},{"pid":"8651c9bf0a7972f2b262d5aabb9c9bcb971622c2","tid":2463836,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03351ca21b3aa7c18746b789d7ad129d78285216","tid":2463836,"uid":188482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ad86e2642222b0b7b3a43add15af5bf3c6d7d74","tid":2463836,"uid":33028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:16:49.000Z","msg":"唔係1月31日開始已經話唔可以用BNO登機?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:18:18.000Z","msg":"個陣應該講緊出境？而家講緊係外國上機？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:19:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202101/29/P2021012900762.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202101%2F29%2FP2021012900762.htm&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWooP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=f8f58f00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202101/29/P2021012900762.htm</a><br />\n隨着外交部今日宣布自一月三十一日起不承認英國國民（海外）護照作為有效旅行證件和身分證明，特區政府將由一月三十一日起採取以下措施：<br />\n<br />\n  （一） 英國國民（海外）護照不能用於在香港出入境，相關香港居民可繼續以其香港特區護照或香港永久性居民身份證用於在香港出入境；<br />\n  （二） 英國國民（海外）護照不得在香港作為任何形式的身分證明，相關香港居民可繼續以其香港永久性居民身份證用作身分證明；<br />\n<span class=\"red\">  （三） 乘客登機前往香港的航班時，航空公司須要求相關香港居民出示其香港特區護照或香港永久性居民身份證，以作證明；</span><br />\n  （四） 未持有其他有效旅行證件的非中國籍香港永久性居民可向入境處申領簽證身分書，以作國際旅行之用。"},{"pid":"8181b281429c5de6f03c0bcc5f2dc1f81ecb41d6","tid":2463836,"uid":42735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:19:54.000Z","msg":"變無國籍即刻入藉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ca51d50bd0407a8d539fcad796e21f32fbc9af","tid":2463836,"uid":258784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:20:29.000Z","msg":"佢真係好想做特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f356176b3e9a20409f688a4ea4ed62c4bf93095f","tid":2463836,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5914d9a279bb74158d949ba9512b84fcca3f501d","tid":2463836,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ad86e2642222b0b7b3a43add15af5bf3c6d7d74","tid":2463836,"uid":33028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:16:49.000Z","msg":"唔係1月31日開始已經話唔可以用BNO登機?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:19:19.000Z","msg":"外國機場登機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202101/29/P2021012900762.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202101%2F29%2FP2021012900762.htm&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWooP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=f8f58f00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202101/29/P2021012900762.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9464b7c91446c7cccfa85e1643530a5c3c068a85","tid":2463836,"uid":11454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:21:44.000Z","msg":"建議港府要求航空公司拒絕以BN(O)申請工作假期簽證的香港永久居民登機返港，必須他們出示身份證或特區護照才放行，反問這樣做「有咩問題」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩野人係用BNO, 但冇身分證？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8696b48978afa3f0dc3c6e482874237ca82b2c9b","tid":2463836,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5ca51d50bd0407a8d539fcad796e21f32fbc9af","tid":2463836,"uid":258784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:20:29.000Z","msg":"佢真係好想做特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:22:17.000Z","